videos.description: Playing in his first game since Aug. 21, 2020, Kristaps Porzingis gets the ball from Luka Doncic and drains a 3-pointer for his first points of the season.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Porzingis scores his first basket of the season) 2021/1/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Porzingis scores his first basket of the season

videos.description: Tim Hardaway Jr. drives through the Hornets' defense and finishes with a dunk.

videos.headline: Hardaway attacks the rim with 1-handed jam

videos.description: Luka Doncic slaps the ball away from Gordon Hayward.  Trey Burke gets it on the other end and drains a 3-pointer.

videos.headline: Luka's great defense leads to a Trey Burke 3

videos.description: Luka Doncic gets a steal and lays it in on the other end, drawing a thumbs-down from one teammate for not dunking it.
